{"id":149350,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/简讯：湖北21县市遭受严重旱灾/","date":"2011-05-02T18:30:26Z","modified":"2011-05-02T18:30:26Z","title":"简讯：湖北21县市遭受严重旱灾","content":"<div>\n<p>中国湖北遭遇了罕见冬春连旱，降水量为50年最少年份，全省21个县市旱情严重。</p>\n<p>据中新社报道，从去年11月以来，湖北大部分地区降水量比常年同期偏少五成，发生了较严重的冬春连旱。</p>\n<p>旱情导致多种农作物生产受到影响。许多地区茶树长不出嫩芽，目前十堰茶叶鲜叶价格已涨至130元/斤。</p>\n<p>当局正在采取紧急措施，设法缓解旱情。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/05/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-mGjYsMKoQnk-w0Zb1EJBob7ycI/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-mGjYsMKoQnk-w0Zb1EJBob7ycI/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-mGjYsMKoQnk-w0Zb1EJBob7ycI/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-mGjYsMKoQnk-w0Zb1EJBob7ycI/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/zuqaoK4mUkQ\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[9012,13228]}